com.google.crypto.tink.jwt

Class Jwt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.crypto.tink.jwt.Jwt

  • @Immutable
public final class Jwt
extends Object
    A read-only implementation of JSON Web Token (JWT).

    A new instance of this class is returned as the result of a sucessfully verification of a JWT.

    See Also:
    JwsMac#verifyMac}

      • getExpiration

        public Instant getExpiration()
        Returns the expiration time claim exp that identifies the instant on or after which the token MUST NOT be accepted for processing or null for none.

        This API requires Instant which is unavailable on Android until API level 26. To use it on older Android devices, enable API desugaring as shown in https://developer.android.com/studio/write/java8-support#library-desugaring.
